Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.72,0:00:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,密会人妻\N内射不伦档案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.68,0:00:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了呢\N你怎么在发呆呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.02,0:00:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思不自觉地就放空了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.22,0:01:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会后悔这次来旅行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.56,0:01:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是没有啦\N但撒谎跑来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.30,0:01:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么谎呢\N骗他说我回老家参加同学聚会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.91,0:01:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吧\N他不会打电话回你家吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.19,0:01:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想是不会啦\N要是会的话就惨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.39,0:01:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老家人说你没回家不就穿帮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.47,0:02:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你是怎么说呢 我说出差\N出差啊 对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.88,0:02:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男生真好 只要说是工作就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.36,0:02:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过很辛苦喔\N辛苦吗 要编很多工作内容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.84,0:02:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能会怀疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.84,0:02:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要有不在场证明\N也是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.66,0:02:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息一下好吗\N好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.73,0:02:58.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近很常开车\N是喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.94,0:03:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法开太久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.48,0:03:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近很久没去旅行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.15,0:03:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很久没旅行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.96,0:03:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会去旅行啊 对啊\N没什么机会去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.44,0:03:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年末年始或中元节之类\N不会去旅行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.78,0:03:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顶多回老家而已吧 是喔\N最近都没旅行 老家而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.99,0:03:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说回老家应该蛮不会被怀疑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.66,0:04:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是有点紧张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.13,0:04:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 有小孩的话可以说跟\N小孩去玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.01,0:04:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以推给小孩就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.62,0:04:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗 可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.63,0:04:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用看没关系吗\N手机吗 不用了 应该是我先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.78,0:05:00.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得来旅行 今天想忘记他\N也是啦 别想太多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.53,0:05:03.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要想太多就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.88,0:05:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以亲嘴吗 好主动\N就想呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.33,0:07:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.08,0:07:33.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好硬喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.24,0:08:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用脱没关系吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.75,0:08:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.91,0:09:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在抽动着喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.83,0:10:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗 很爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.98,0:11:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔也脱掉好吗\N好热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.60,0:21:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.28,0:22:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再继续旅行吧\N继续吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.72,0:22:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里很安静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.39,0:22:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次来这种地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.66,0:22:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前都是去那些地方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.33,0:22:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没住过什么旅馆耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.47,0:23:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅行都会来旅馆居多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.34,0:23:17.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里还有露天温泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.42,0:23:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是混浴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.43,0:23:24.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混浴吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.56,0:23:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也还没问\N要跟饭店确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.18,0:23:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得来\N等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:21.95,0:25:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:35.56,0:25:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:41.57,0:25:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起洗澡吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:27.61,0:26:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要在意摄影机\N我会害羞耶 放心没人在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:38.16,0:26:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很漂亮 \N不要看啦 超美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:43.29,0:27:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好开心 真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:49.56,0:27:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉很特别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:55.70,0:28:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露天温泉还不习惯\N但很爽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:03.57,0:28:10.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对皮皮肤好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:16.79,0:28:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:21.73,0:28:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:20.44,0:31:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:17.69,0:32:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害羞吗 都看光了了\N还会害羞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:29.84,0:32:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:01.74,0:33:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:14.21,0:34:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁股也要洗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:53.05,0:34:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是洗一洗而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:25.14,0:36:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗干净了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:11.90,0:40:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁股面对我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:00.04,0:47:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快帮我吹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:24.47,0:56:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗\N很爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:18.51,0:59:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换个姿势
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:46.32,1:02:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射好多\N很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:18.49,1:03:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在看什么\N这里很漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:26.63,1:03:32.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很美吧 这里\N真开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:43.58,1:03:49.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很适合这里\N是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:51.85,1:03:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:05.47,1:04:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高跟鞋没关系吗 没关系\N不会难走吗 不会
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:19.88,1:04:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两人一起走在这里不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:27.49,1:04:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:30.29,1:04:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待什么呢\N今天一起住 是啊 机会难得
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:42.57,1:04:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待什么呢\N温泉 还有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:57.52,1:05:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,料理 也是\N还有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:08.86,1:05:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能说\N有不能说的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:16.87,1:05:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很期待吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:35.16,1:05:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗完澡之后\N还有很多时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:56.78,1:05:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近很少喝酒吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:00.38,1:06:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近很少机会喝 是喔\N对啊 很久没喝 穿这样真好看 适合你 很美
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:24.14,1:06:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是旅馆的人借我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:32.01,1:06:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是自己的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:37.75,1:06:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:42.82,1:06:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿这样去看烟火不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:50.83,1:06:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢吗\N当然啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:04.05,1:07:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,性感喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:09.38,1:07:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好看 真的吗\N平常会穿吗 不常耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:16.19,1:07:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前会穿 真的啊\N最近不会穿 那会穿内衣吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:29.40,1:07:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内衣吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:34.34,1:07:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时穿有时不穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:39.01,1:07:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:56.10,1:08:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要摸摸 看不知道耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:05.97,1:08:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,材质不错喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:15.85,1:08:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:20.52,1:08:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:30.53,1:08:34.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有摸到喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:48.55,1:08:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以脱下来让我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:00.03,1:09:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是想像就很性感
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:56.88,1:09:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有穿内衣喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:47.53,1:11:55.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带来的 为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:56.00,1:12:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:57.85,1:14:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:46.97,1:15:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁股好翘喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:16.86,1:16:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:34.87,1:18:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面对我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:07.65,1:27:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿着
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:44.60,1:29:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想睡了 喝了很多酒\N这感觉不错 很悠闲
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:08.50,1:30:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很爽 第一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:12.37,1:30:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露天风是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:15.44,1:30:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到那么爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:19.31,1:30:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初体验吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:24.51,1:30:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很爽吧 很棒的回忆\N但明天就要回去了 好快
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:00.53,1:44:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮\N讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:03.06,1:55:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:26.67,1:57:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:55.36,1:57:58.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:22.91,1:59:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽 好棒 怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:34.13,1:59:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:33.22,2:04:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:21:52.80,2:21:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好深 好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:23:35.57,2:23:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射好多
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:24:11.87,2:24:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了 射很远
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:24:19.21,2:24:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再去洗一次吧\N好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:24:36.69,2:24:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样无法睡吧\N对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:24:47.90,2:24:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好吧
